item.title: Recording available: Microsoft Graph September Community call - Provisioning demo
item.author: vbiret+blog@outlook.com (Vincent Biret)
item.description: Last September I was invited to speak again on the Microsoft Graph Community call. If you don’t know about it, this free online monthly call brings together Microsoft Product Team members and Community members demonstrating new capabilities and real world examples. It is a great way to catch up on the latest news and I highly recommend you attend it if you work with the Microsoft Graph or would like to.
